# Skills

Reusable procedural knowledge for AI agents working in this project.

## Structure

Each skill lives in its own directory with a `SKILL.md` file:

```
skills/
  my-skill/
    SKILL.md       # Required: name, description, trigger in frontmatter
    references/    # Optional: supporting files
    scripts/       # Optional: executable scripts
```

## SKILL.md Format

```yaml
---
name: my-skill
description: One-line summary of what this skill does
trigger: when to activate this skill
---

# My Skill

Detailed instructions for the agent.
```

## Progressive Disclosure

- Skill names and descriptions are always loaded into agent context
- Full skill body is loaded only when the skill is activated
- Keep descriptions concise (one line) for efficient context usage
